Joel de la Fuente https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joel_de_la_Fuente 0 Joel de la Fuente (born April 21, 1969) is an American actor. He first gained recognition for his role as 1st Lieutenant Paul Wang in Space: Above and Beyond, and is best known for his roles as Dr. Johann Pryce in Hemlock Grove, Kenpeitai Chief Inspector Takeshi Kido in The Man in the High Castle and recurring appearances on Law Order: Special Victims Unit as Technical Assistance Response UnitTech Ruben Morales.
